title: Neha Kakkar performs at Butler House in Delhi
text:
Delhiites showed off their love for music at recent event at Butler House, hosted by Akshay Kakkar, Sabhay Juneja and Rohit Bhatia.
It was a star-studded music launch event that saw performances by singers like Neha Kakkar, Abhijeet Sawant, rapper AJ Singh and Shweta Sharma. Guests like Twinkle Kakkar and Suruchi Bhatia turned up to congratulate the owners and enjoy the Bollywood performances.
Akshay Kakkar said, "Butler House is all set to entertain Delhi with best of the gigs lined up. We'll make sure that if food, beverages and entertainment is what your are looking for, then this is the place for you."
